---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Section from "../components/common/Section.astro";
import Anchor from "../components/common/Anchor.astro";
---

<Layout>
  <Fragment slot="head">
    <title>Apply for Free 1-on-1 Coaching (6-Week Beta Program) • Nathan Laundry</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Coaching for tech students and early-career folks seeking clarity, meaning, and direction. Apply for a free 6-week beta program." />
    <link rel="canonical" href="https://nathanlaundry.com/coaching" />
  </Fragment>

  <Section class="py-16 text-center bg-gradient-to-b from-base-100 to-base-200/50">
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 flex items-center justify-center gap-3">
      🧭 Coaching for People Who Want Their Work to Mean Something
    </h1>
    <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-base-content/70 mb-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
      You're not burned out because you can't keep up.<br/>
      You're burned out because you actually give a damn — and you're tired of being told to just work harder.
    </p>
    <div class="flex justify-center">
      <Anchor url="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeCux2ip1jRF1fVUb2IacsCAkyWXR0BJ-CvNffWsnZuOsT6pw/viewform?usp=dialog" external={true} class="btn btn-primary btn-lg text-lg px-8 py-4 mt-4 animate-pulse" aria-label="Apply for Coaching">
        🔗 Apply Now
      </Anchor>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <Section class="py-12">
    <div class="bg-base-200/30 rounded-lg p-8 border border-base-300">
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-semibold mb-6 text-center">
        You don't need another Notion dashboard.<br/>
        You need a reason to get up in the morning.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg mb-6 text-center">
        This is for you if you're a student/early-career professional in tech AND:
      </p>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="bg-base-100 rounded-lg p-6 border border-base-300">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">🔨 You love building things</h3>
          <p class="text-base-content/80">But want your work to matter — not just ship features for the sake of it.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-base-100 rounded-lg p-6 border border-base-300">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">🏃‍♂️ You're tired of Big Tech's hamster wheel</h3>
          <p class="text-base-content/80">No more building for companies you don't believe in.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-base-100 rounded-lg p-6 border border-base-300">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">⚡ You feel squeezed by hustle culture</h3>
          <p class="text-base-content/80">Productivity hacks haven't made life better (and you're over it).</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-base-100 rounded-lg p-6 border border-base-300">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">🎯 You want a life that feels meaningful</h3>
          <p class="text-base-content/80">You want your work to do something good, not just pad your resume</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="text-xl font-bold text-center mt-8 text-primary">
        You've optimized your workflow.<br/>
        Now it's time to optimize for meaning.
      </p>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <Section class="py-12">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-8">How It Works</h2>
    <p class="text-lg text-center mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      Over six 1-on-1 sessions, we'll cut through the noise and get clear on:
    </p>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="bg-base-100 rounded-lg p-6 border border-base-300 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
        <div class="text-2xl mb-3">⚡</div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Energy Audit</h3>
        <p class="text-base-content/80">What's actually draining you (and why more "hustle" isn't the answer).</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-base-100 rounded-lg p-6 border border-base-300 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
        <div class="text-2xl mb-3">🎯</div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Values Clarity</h3>
        <p class="text-base-content/80">What values you truly want your life and work to reflect.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-base-100 rounded-lg p-6 border border-base-300 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
        <div class="text-2xl mb-3">📅</div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Day Design</h3>
        <p class="text-base-content/80">How to structure your days so you don't burn out or lose yourself.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-base-100 rounded-lg p-6 border border-base-300 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
        <div class="text-2xl mb-3">🌱</div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Sustainable Growth</h3>
        <p class="text-base-content/80">How to slow down, stay human, and still keep growing — without getting sucked into performative overwork.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-base-100 rounded-lg p-6 border border-base-300 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
        <div class="text-2xl mb-3">📝</div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Life README</h3>
        <p class="text-base-content/80">How to write a personal README — so you can make decisions when things get loud or confusing.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <Section class="py-12 bg-base-200/30">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Why I'm Doing This</h2>
          <div class="space-y-4 text-lg">
            <p>I've been the overachieving CS student.</p>
            <p>I've been the grad student collecting credentials "just in case."</p>
            <p>I've chased security, hit the wall, and had to figure out what a meaningful life in tech looks like while managing uncertainty.</p>
          </div>
          <p class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 text-primary">
            This isn't about "crushing it."<br/>
            It's about thinking deeply, structuring your days with intention, and building a life you're actually proud of.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-base-100 rounded-lg p-8 border border-base-300">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-center">What It Costs</h3>
          <div class="text-center mb-6">
            <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-primary mb-2">$0</div>
            <p class="text-lg">Right now</p>
          </div>
          <p class="mb-4">
            This is a free beta. I'm taking on 2–3 clients this fall to refine the program. All I ask for is honest feedback — and, if it helps you, a testimonial.
          </p>
          <p class="text-base-content/80 text-center font-medium">
            No sales funnel. No upsell. No bullshit.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <Section class="py-16 text-center">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">How to Apply</h2>
    <p class="text-xl mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      If you're reading this and thinking, "Yes — this is what I've been missing," fill out the form.<br/>
      I'll read every application myself, and if it feels like a good fit, we'll talk.
    </p>
    <Anchor url="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeCux2ip1jRF1fVUb2IacsCAkyWXR0BJ-CvNffWsnZuOsT6pw/viewform?usp=dialog" external={true} class="btn btn-primary btn-lg text-xl px-10 py-4 animate-pulse" aria-label="Apply for Coaching">
      🔗 Apply Now
    </Anchor>
  </Section>

  <Section class="py-12 bg-gradient-to-b from-base-200/30 to-base-100">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Final Note</h2>
      <div class="space-y-4 text-lg leading-relaxed">
        <p>You can love tech and still want more out of life than just "shipped code."</p>
        <p>You can care about your work and also about who you become while doing it.</p>
        <p>You don't need to hustle harder. You just need clarity — and a little help finding it.</p>
      </div>
      <p class="text-xl font-bold mt-8 text-primary">
        Let's talk,<br/>Nathan
      </p>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <Section class="py-8 bg-base-200/50">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="bg-base-100 rounded-lg p-6 border border-base-300">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-4 text-center">Disclaimer</h3>
        <p class="text-base-content/80 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          This coaching program is not therapy, counselling, or mental health treatment. I'm not a licensed therapist or counsellor. Coaching is focused on personal growth, clarity, and building systems for meaningful work and life. If you're experiencing significant mental health challenges, please reach out to a qualified mental health professional.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>

</Layout>
